{
  "$schema": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/DjobaDELATV/seygo_data/main/schema/v1/card.json",
  "id": "136fc2fa-f0f7-4b93-a508-5f5d35de0553",
  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Cyber Angel Benten",
      "effect": "You can Ritual Summon this card with \"Machine Angel Ritual\". If this card destroys a monster by battle and sends it to the GY: Inflict damage to your opponent equal to that monster's original DEF in the GY. If this card is Tributed: You can add 1 LIGHT Fairy monster from your Deck to your hand."
    },
    "fr": {
      "name": "Ange Cyber Benten",
      "effect": "Vous pouvez Invoquer Rituellement cette carte avec \"Rituel de l'Ange Machine\". Si cette carte d\u00e9truit un monstre au combat et l'envoie au Cimeti\u00e8re : infligez des dommages \u00e0 votre adversaire \u00e9gaux \u00e0 la DEF d'origine du monstre dans le Cimeti\u00e8re. Si cette carte est Sacrifi\u00e9e : vous pouvez ajouter 1 monstre LUMI\u00c8RE Elfe depuis votre Deck \u00e0 votre main."
    },
    "de": {
      "name": "Cyberengel - Benten",
      "effect": "Du kannst diese Karte mit \u201eMaschinenengel-Ritual\u201c als Ritualbeschw\u00f6rung beschw\u00f6ren. Falls diese Karte ein Monster durch Kampf zerst\u00f6rt und auf den Friedhof legt: F\u00fcge deinem Gegner Schaden in H\u00f6he der Grund-DEF jenes Monsters im Friedhof zu. Falls diese Karte als Tribut angeboten wird: Du kannst deiner Hand 1 LICHT Fee-Monster von deinem Deck hinzuf\u00fcgen."
    },
    "it": {
      "name": "Cyber Angelo Benten",
      "effect": "Puoi Evocare tramite Rituale questa carta con \"Rituale dell'Angelo Macchina\". Se questa carta distrugge un mostro in battaglia e lo manda al Cimitero: infliggi al tuo avversario danno pari al DEF originale di quel mostro nel Cimitero. Se questa carta viene offerta come Tributo: puoi aggiungere 1 mostro LUCE Fata dal tuo Deck alla tua mano."
    },
    "pt": {
      "name": "Ciber Anja Benten",
      "effect": "Voc\u00ea pode Invocar este card por Invoca\u00e7\u00e3o-Ritual com \"Ritual M\u00e1quina de Anjo\". Se este card destruir um monstro em batalha e envi\u00e1-lo para o Cemit\u00e9rio: cause dano ao seu oponente igual \u00e0 DEF original desse monstro no Cemit\u00e9rio. Se este card for oferecido como Tributo: voc\u00ea pode adicionar 1 monstro Fada de LUZ do seu Deck \u00e0 sua m\u00e3o."
    },
    "es": {
      "name": "Ciber \u00c1ngel Benten",
      "effect": "Puedes Invocar esta carta por Ritual con \"Ritual del \u00c1ngel Mec\u00e1nico\". Si esta carta destruye un monstruo en batalla y lo manda al Cementerio: inflige da\u00f1o a tu adversario igual a la DEF original de ese monstruo en el Cementerio. Si esta carta es Sacrificada: puedes a\u00f1adir a tu mano 1 monstruo Hada de LUZ en tu Deck."
    },
    "ja": {
      "name": "\u30b5\u30a4\u30d0\u30fc\u30fb\u30a8\u30f3\u30b8\u30a7\u30eb\uff0d\u5f01\u5929\uff0d",
      "effect": "\u300c\u6a5f\u68b0\u5929\u4f7f\u306e\u5100\u5f0f\u300d\u306b\u3088\u308a\u964d\u81e8\u3002\u2460\uff1a\u3053\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u304c\u6226\u95d8\u3067\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u3092\u7834\u58ca\u3057\u5893\u5730\u3078\u9001\u3063\u305f\u5834\u5408\u306b\u767a\u52d5\u3059\u308b\u3002\u305d\u306e\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u306e\u5143\u3005\u306e\u5b88\u5099\u529b\u5206\u306e\u30c0\u30e1\u30fc\u30b8\u3092\u76f8\u624b\u306b\u4e0e\u3048\u308b\u3002\u2461\uff1a\u3053\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u304c\u30ea\u30ea\u30fc\u30b9\u3055\u308c\u305f\u5834\u5408\u306b\u767a\u52d5\u3067\u304d\u308b\u3002\u30c7\u30c3\u30ad\u304b\u3089\u5929\u4f7f\u65cf\u30fb\u5149\u5c5e\u6027\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\uff11\u4f53\u3092\u624b\u672d\u306b\u52a0\u3048\u308b\u3002"
    },
    "ko": {
      "name": "\uc0ac\uc774\ubc84 \uc5d4\uc824\uff0d\ubca4\ud150\uff0d",
      "effect": "\"\uae30\uacc4\ucc9c\uc0ac\uc758 \uc758\uc2dd\"\uc5d0 \uc758\ud574 \uc758\uc2dd \uc18c\ud658\n\u2460: \uc774 \uce74\ub4dc\uac00 \uc804\ud22c\ub85c \ubaac\uc2a4\ud130\ub97c \ud30c\uad34\ud558\uace0 \ubb18\uc9c0\ub85c \ubcf4\ub0c8\uc744 \uacbd\uc6b0\uc5d0 \ubc1c\ub3d9\ud55c\ub2e4. \uadf8 \ubaac\uc2a4\ud130\uc758 \uc6d0\ub798 \uc218\ube44\ub825\ub9cc\ud07c\uc758 \ub370\ubbf8\uc9c0\ub97c \uc0c1\ub300\uc5d0\uac8c \uc900\ub2e4. \u2461: \uc774 \uce74\ub4dc\uac00 \ub9b4\ub9ac\uc2a4\ub418\uc5c8\uc744 \uacbd\uc6b0\uc5d0 \ubc1c\ub3d9\ud560 \uc218 \uc788\ub2e4. \ub371\uc5d0\uc11c \ucc9c\uc0ac\uc871 / \ube5b \uc18d\uc131 \ubaac\uc2a4\ud130 1\uc7a5\uc744 \ud328\uc5d0 \ub123\ub294\ub2e4."
    },
    "zh-CN": {
